title: Fan Case And Bag, 19th century
medium:
Medium: canvas, silk, ribbon, glass bead
Technique: embroidered in tent stitch
dimensions:
H x W (case): 30 x 6 cm (11 3/4 x 2 3/8 in.)
H x diam. (bag): 50 x 4 cm (19 5/8 x 1 1/2 in.)
creditline: Gift of Mrs. R. Keith Kane from the Estate of Mrs. Robert B. Noyes
description: Long narrow case for spectacles and small circular  case cover (or bag) embroidered in tent stitch in design of birds and flowers. Blue satin linings, blue ribbons with pink glass beads join the two objects.
